content: The destination already contains files with the same name.

comment.text: The translation key "FilesAlreadyContains" is used to display a message when adding files to a destination that already contains files with the same name. This message appears in a dialog box when trying to resolve conflicts while uploading or importing files.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'الوجهة تحتوي بالفعل على ملفات بنفس الاسم' is a literal translation and while understandable, it doesn't sound entirely natural in Arabic. A more idiomatic phrasing would be preferable.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: الوجهة تحتوي على ملفات بنفس الاسم بالفعل. (Al-wijha tuḥtawi ʿala malaffat bi nafs al-ism bil-fiʿl.) - This emphasizes 'already' more naturally.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase "files with the same name" is not perfectly conveyed by "նույն անունով ֆայլեր:" A more accurate translation would consider the *exact* match of both name and potentially other attributes (like size or timestamp) to avoid ambiguity. While 'same name' is the core meaning, a more precise rendering could strengthen the message in a technical context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider phrasing it as: «Նպատակակետն արդեն պարունակում է նույն անունով և հատկանիշներով ֆայլեր» (The destination already contains files with the same name and attributes) or a similar construction emphasizing a more complete match.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Romanian translation 'Fișiere cu acelaşi nume există deja la destinație' is grammatically correct, but could be slightly more fluent. A more natural phrasing would be 'Există deja fișiere cu același nume în destinație.'
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Există deja fișiere cu același nume în destinație.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ගමනාන්තයේ දැනටමත් එකම නමින් ගොනු අඩංගු වේ.' is a literal translation and may not be the most natural or idiomatic way to express the meaning in Sinhala. A more natural phrasing might emphasize that the file cannot be copied.

The translation 'Hedef zaten aynı ada sahip dosyalar içeriyor.' is a literal translation that doesn't fully capture the nuance of 'The destination already contains files with the same name.' It sounds slightly awkward in Turkish. A more natural and idiomatic translation would convey the same meaning more effectively.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Hedefte aynı isimli dosyalar zaten mevcut.
